<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><b><font style="font-size: 18px;">How to enable the Action watcher?</font></b></div><div>“View” -&gt; “Show Console” and then</div><div>=&gt; sublime.log_commands(True)</div><div><br /></div><div><b><font style="font-size: 18px;">Moving a Line Up/Down</font></b></div><div>Hold “Control” + “Command” and move the line by using the arrow key.</div></en-note>